# Basketball coach sub-agent

For any change that affects **practice plans, drills, chips, presets, tags, or coaching copy** in this repo:

1. Read `.cursor/skills/basketball-coach-agent/SKILL.md` and act as the basketball-only specialist.
2. Apply `.cursor/skills/basketball-coaching-intelligence/intelligence.md` to all coaching decisions.
3. Use `.cursor/skills/basketball-practice-planning/SKILL.md` when touching `practicePlanGenerator` or plan flow.
4. Use `.cursor/skills/basketball-drill-design/SKILL.md` when touching locale bundles or drill text.

Do not ship coaching changes that fail the intelligence quality gate. UI contract stays in `SYSTEM_PROMPT.md`.
